[The headline of this posting demonstrates a small flurry of official
reports of new Avian influenza activity. These 3 new reports, combined with
an update report from Viet Nam (indicating spread to a new province),
represent a clear upsurge in official OIE reporting compared with the past
few months. - Mod.PC]
